condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Section II.B.3 | Description :Borrower shall have financial statements audited by independent auditors and auditstandards acceptable to Bank, to be furrnished no later than 6 months after end of period. | Due Date :31-Dec-2017

Finance Agreement :Section V.1 | Description :Borrower to maintain its accounts receivable at a level not exceeding an amountequivalent to the proceeds of its transmission and other regulated services for the 3 preceeding months | Frequency :Monthly

Finance Agreement :Section V.2 | Description :Borrower to maintain funds from internal cash generation equivalent to not less than20% of annual average capital expenditure incurred during previous, current and following FY | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :Section V.3 | Description :Borrower shall maintain a debt to equity ratio not greater than 4 to 1 | Frequency:Yearly
